<P>THE GRAY's-INN JOURNAL.</P>
<P>IN TWO VOLUMES.</P>
<P>VOL. I.</P>
<Q>Non fuit Con&s;ilium &s;ocordi&acirc; atque de&s;idi&acirc; bo|num otium conterere.
<BIBL>SALLUST.</BIBL></Q>
<Q>Eye Nature's Walks, &s;hoot Folly as it flies, And catch the Manners living, as they ri&s;e.
<BIBL>POPE.</BIBL></Q>
