<L>Come, 'tis worth the Experiment&mdash;&s;avour his Play.</L>
<L>Full five Stories high he has mounted his Hopes,</L>
<L>But Critics take care,&mdash;he's on a Ladder of Ropes;</L>
<L>Should ye cut but one Cord, you'll cru&s;h all his Bones;</L>
<L>Adieu Bricklayer and Bard,&mdash;there's an end of poor JONES.</L>
</SP>
